{"tid":1405392,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰績彪炳]細數TVB三大厹","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:22:00.000Z","uid":256585,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7379474064cc8bfd3191a4c427ed12b1650a466b","tid":1405392,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"俗語有話喺度食就唔好喺度屙<br />\n我地一齊回帶<br />\n睇下TVB食女無數嘅三大狗公<br />\n到底有幾風流會有幾折墮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\nTop1 張致恆<br />\n<br />\n張致恆出道16年情史多籮籮　11段戀情多因偷食導致分手<br />\n<br />\n【復仇聯盟】張致恆同一條短訊轉發不同女友Steven三名舊愛出面力數渣男</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ygy9syi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgy9syi.png&h=b6e06a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6r3abMB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6r3abMB.png&h=c205228a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWqvWdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWqvWdS.png&h=7f4d1690&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4n4TT0y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4n4TT0y.png&h=9cd56e01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdkWRMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdkWRMC.png&h=6486ea9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ZCaWdi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZCaWdi.png&h=120ab779&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6E2usjZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6E2usjZ.png&h=bc271df9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eTxqkF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eTxqkF.png&h=a637d38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">戰績<br />\n2001年黃榕<br />\n2004年傅又宣（傅珮嘉）<br />\n2006年女網友Fiona<br />\n2007年鍾舒漫<br />\n2013年漏M女孫旗/莊端兒/裕美/莊家旻<br />\n2016年台妹Doris<br />\n2017年梁皓恩（April）<br />\n2019年雯雯/Moon/C小姐/S小姐</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7T6V7y4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7T6V7y4.png&h=93bc3a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">樂極生悲！Boy'z張致恆剛宣佈婚訊，就被小四小五曝一腳踏六船</span><br />\n<br />\n________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\nTop2 魏焌皓<br />\n<br />\n魏焌皓男女通吃被爆口技了得黃榕：賤過陳冠希！ <br />\n<br />\n【突然消失】魏焌皓被大台炒魷 與麥明詩拍《使徒2》傳犯不當行為</span></span><br />\n<br />\n備受大台力捧的「大隻仔」魏焌皓，最近被指一腳踏兩船，偷嗒o靚模黃榕及o靚妹（李綺雯），之後o趙完鬆，男方更因拒認風流帳與黃榕展開罵戰。 外表純情的魏焌皓，憑 40吋胸肌及油腔滑調，兩年內速食 15o靚模、花旦，集郵名單拍得住陳冠希。 <br />\n<br />\n記者發現他一個月內連嗒黃榕、蔡思貝、唐貝詩、趙哲妤、o靚妹，更電埋綠魔及鄭紹康為他r job。家住公屋的魏焌皓雖然冇財，但憑好身材一樣男女通殺。被用完即棄的黃榕，?爆鬧佢花心︰「佢仲賤過 Edison（陳冠希）！」至於綠魔則讚他「口技超凡」。看來，魏焌皓真是有獨特的過人之處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gv2m2Sa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgv2m2Sa.png&h=83e8c641&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zPOhBca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzPOhBca.png&h=52f1774c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cW2RFDR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcW2RFDR.png&h=737f3a34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/58pkyYS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F58pkyYS.png&h=0297958f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09xeDqy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09xeDqy.png&h=c34a2832&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zODQWcd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzODQWcd.png&h=6a5491fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZADkDU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZADkDU.png&h=b828813e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6Jp0DV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6Jp0DV.png&h=5a509df9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOiNdYW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOiNdYW.png&h=84ef6062&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W5QjPxh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW5QjPxh.png&h=947707f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最爆係咩？係張致恆前女友都俾魏焌皓食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wx2Kgct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWx2Kgct.png&h=f9a67940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魏焌皓更雜食唔少知名度一般的o靚模（如莊端兒），收她們做契妹，經常借意親近她們。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">戰績<br />\n2012年-2018年<br />\n黃榕/李綺雯/蔡思貝/唐貝詩/歐陽巧盈/趙哲妤/朱晨麗/朱千雪/羅彩鈴/不知名𡃁模 x N咁多個/陳潔玲/尹詩沛/張慧雯/想食麥明詩</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yHRFLw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yHRFLw.png&h=38b1d5fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">魏焌皓除咗麥明詩事件外原來當年陳潔玲爆TVB人渣原來係佢</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mhVClma-e0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmhVClma-e0k&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=bfe003fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mhVClma-e0k</a>"},{"pid":"b544795fd3786180d0bb9db916220a9cee0b17d5","tid":1405392,"uid":256585,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\nTop3 周志文<br />\n<br />\n「大食」周志文屢勸不改　樂易玲落令炒魷<br />\n<br />\n周志文堪稱TVB「集郵王」 9大緋聞女友個個女神級</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「巨聲大孖」周志文，○九年出道至今，食女多過做嘢！一一年跟有米女友 CoCo袁聖殷撻着同居，就算有人照顧，但返內地和馬賽合作拍劇又搞上；一腳踏兩船小兒科，食女癮大的他，近年更連環𠝹五女，偷食發電機蔡思貝外，更被目擊跟劉佩玥（ Moon）在夜店狂嘴，同時間又對陳瀅、吳若希以及何雁詩狂攻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxBvbSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxBvbSZ.png&h=63171b72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2aK40Mk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2aK40Mk.png&h=a213cee1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DoNNYx0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDoNNYx0.png&h=8f6e0272&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiJabS1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiJabS1.png&h=cba207ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RsmGiy3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsmGiy3.png&h=da46cc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MW2x9GT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMW2x9GT.png&h=e9132b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JF0y85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JF0y85.png&h=0fdd3832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2BbFP4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2BbFP4.png&h=097760e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5AvWoq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5AvWoq.png&h=a2bdc3ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JpADkSA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJpADkSA.png&h=4be13c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">戰績<br />\n1.巨聲出身狂痴王嘉儀<br />\n2.有米CoCo照顧<br />\n3.陪何雁詩旅行<br />\n4.借玩狗溝陳瀅<br />\n5.胡杏兒三亞拍戲男主人上身<br />\n6.蔡思貝台灣過夜/公屋偷歡<br />\n7.假戲真做馬賽<br />\n8.同莊思明行街睇戲超市溫馨濕平<br />\n9.探病搏吳若希好感<br />\n10.沙灘放狗 狂嘴劉佩玥</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWWZPJj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWWZPJj.png&h=7992446b&s={SIZE}\" /